    COMMENT: ====================================================================================
    COMMENT: SESSION MANAGEMENT METHOD
    COMMENT: ====================================================================================
    
    COMMENT: Clears session-specific data to return the session to an unauthenticated state.
    METHOD clearSessionData()
        
        PURPOSE: Clears user authentication data while keeping the session structure intact
        
        WHY: Called by AppState.getSessionStatus() when a session expires or is cancelled,
             and by AppState.clearSession() when logging out
        
        BEHAVIOR:
            SET this.id TO null
            SET this.user TO null
            SET this.passport_url TO null
            SET this.expired TO false
            SET this.remember TO false
            SET this.verified TO false
    END METHOD
